author: rcm
msg: The distribution data factory now deals with cyclical transient graphs.  Each data object is now created without its fields, and added to a map.  Any repeated attempt to reference the same object result in the same data object being used.  This required the content of the object to set up later, hence the a change to the ObjectData interface.

author: rcm
msg: The object store persistor was not shutting down the persist algorithm.  Now it is is.
